data.title: Coffee Break Spanish Magazine Season 1
data.meta_description: Keep your Spanish up to scratch with the Coffee Break Spanish Magazine
data.text:
This course includes:

10 audio lessons

10 video interviews

Comprehensive lesson notes with grammar explanations

Vocabulary lists

Downloadable files for offline use

Learn with a worldwide community of learners

One off payment

Lifetime access to all lessons

Please note that this price is inclusive of all tax, including VAT. With this one-off payment, each of the 40 lessons included in the course will cost you less than a cup of coffee in most coffee shops!
